{"tid":1686911,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"沈振盈大概有幾多身家？","createTime":"2019-11-01T12:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:54:19.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7a36e36230aed4c4c778cf74eb56f24c2dbd4d","tid":1686911,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"成日講到頭頭是道 <br />\n好似睇穿晒個股市 <br />\n咁實際上有幾多身家先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7d0ef02bddddbcdb3b89df69e52764e3b63a84","tid":1686911,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署 】依個就快截止⚠️<br />\n1. 制裁TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32jy4fj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32jy4fj&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=79a9536c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32jy4fj</a><br />\n尚欠60000人聯署，11月9日截止。<br />\n2. 解散警隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/31gWPHR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31gWPHR&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=5fc4228b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/31gWPHR</a><br />\n尚欠 16000 人聯署，11 月 9日截止。<br />\n簽&gt;記得email確認&gt;傳開去"},{"pid":"449065403a89b8c212982c6dc5e3e3c32df26eaf","tid":1686911,"uid":75778,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"0.5"},{"pid":"12d21a2d8eb86ec4fae3eaf9abe84304ad1813ed","tid":1686911,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449065403a89b8c212982c6dc5e3e3c32df26eaf","tid":1686911,"uid":75778,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"0.5"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"5毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37af0d463d7e94b89b5611da5d457917bc69bd0","tid":1686911,"uid":72734,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"大膽<img src=\"/asse